.modal-footer
	.save-area
		.alert.alert-success.alert-dismissible(role='alert' ng-show='evMonthCtrl.formSuccess')
			button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='alert', aria-label='Close')
				span(aria-hidden='true')
					i.glyphicon.glyphicon-remove
			strong Success!
			|  You've just saved the event! Check the calendar now.
		.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-xs-6
			button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit' ng-disabled="newEventForm.$invalid" ng-click="evMonthCtrl.submitModal()") Save
		.col-md-6.col-sm-6
			button.btn.btn-default(ng-click="evMonthCtrl.closeModal()") Cancel